                            <comment id="13193943" author="vsg" created="Thu, 26 Jan 2012 16:26:09 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Known workaround:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For HTTPTransportFactory, we force its initialization, when bus is being initialized in our CXFBusFactory implementation, and before anyone uses the HTTPTransportFactory:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;            DestinationFactoryManager mgr = bus.getExtension(DestinationFactoryManager.class);&lt;br/&gt;
            mgr.getDestinationFactory(&quot;http://cxf.apache.org/transports/http&quot;);&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
